flowRoot.flowPara: Potentially 0.2mm too big. Made it fit though.

The light enclosure. A 3x3 grid. Interior grid separators and back are made of 3/16" foam cork board (rigid and cheap) and outer (top) and sides (the only thing visible) are made of 1/8" black acrylic.
For a nice detail I also cut out of the grid and mounted it to the top of the transparent white acrylic.
